-27-13-52-59-1024x597.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59.png.webp 1169w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a>Hani, from <a href=\"https://servarica.com/\">Servarica</a>, has written us to share these improved offers with you for DDoS-protected Xen VPS in Montreal, Canada. These servers enjoy DDoS protection up to 10Gbps and 8M pps.</p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>2GB Xen</strong><p></p><ul><li>2.5GB RAM</li><li>1 abusive CPU core</li><li>25GB SSD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>IPv6 available</li><li>XenPV/Custom</li><li>$7/month</li><li><a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=223\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td><strong>1GB Xen</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU core</li><li>12GB SSD space</li><li>0.5TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>IPv6 available</li><li>XenPV/Custom</li><li>$4.50/month</li><li><a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=224\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>We\u2019ve featured Servarica several times before. Since last time their offers have gotten considerably more interesting. There\u2019s now a $7/2GB offer that includes a CPU core than may be used as much as you want. Their 1GB offer has seen its price lowered to just $4.50/month. Such offers including DDoS protection (not with OVH) are really quite interesting if you ask me. Host nodes have dual 6-core AMD CPUs and have several Pure SSDs in them. These offers run on a pool of xensever nodes with the aforementioned specifications. There were some positive reviews on their last offers from long-time customers, so you should be save with these guys. As always, feel free to share your experiences as well!</p><p><span id=\"more-6510\"></span></p><p>Payments are possible via PayPal, credit card, and Payza. Orders coming from a proxy or VPN IP will not be accepted and neither will 